      "content": "i know people are trying, but it feels like they're just rearranging deck chairs on the titanic. the math doesn't add up. the damage is already done. it's hard to care about \"making a difference\" when the end result is inevitable. it just feels like a huge, exhausting lie we tell ourselves to keep going. it's exhausting.",
